N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4605.2 - Report of net profits

State Regulations

The license of any organization, licensed to conduct
games of chance, that does not report net profits during any one-year period or
as otherwise required may be denied, suspended or revoked. Notes
